Full_rankings=left_join(Rankings, Points, by="Player")%>%
  select(-"Team.y")%>%
  rename("Rank"="Rank.x", "PointsRank"="Rank.y", "AverageRank"="Avg.x", "AveragePoints"="Avg.y", "Team"="Team.x")%>%
  separate(Pos, c("Pos", "Number"), sep = "RB|WR|TE|QB|K|DST") %>%
  select(-"Pos", -"WSID")%>%
  mutate(Number=as.numeric(Number))
  

Full_rankings=Full_rankings[,c(1:4,14,5:13,15:17)]
Full_rankings=Full_rankings[-(495:498),]
Full_rankings
write.csv(Full_rankings, "Full_rankings.csv")
Full_rankings%>%
  filter(Position=="RB")%>%
  ggplot()+geom_point(aes(x=Tier, y=AveragePoints))

Full_rankings%>%
  filter(Position=="RB")%>%
  arrange((Number))%>%
  ggplot(mapping=aes(x=Number, y=AveragePoints))+geom_point()+geom_smooth()
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess' and formula 'y ~ x'
